    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my reliable ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape and has been well-loved, perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the new-car price tag. Everything runs smoothly, and it's ready for its next adventure! Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46-generation M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This unit is paired with the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and fresh bushings across the multi-link rear suspension to restore factory-spec kinematics. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with spirited use, the powertrain remains exceptionally tight, delivering linear power up to the 8,000 RPM redline. This is a driver-focused example with the major mechanical hurdles already addressed for the next enthusiast owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. No major issues.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
