      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with comfort. The exterior finish retains a high gloss, showing only minor signs of standard road use, while the alloy wheels are free of major scuffs. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the premium leather seats are supple without any rips or thinning, and the dashboard remains crack-free. All technological features, including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a documented service history. It has recently received a fresh synthetic oil change and a new set of tires. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts crisply, and the suspension provides a quiet, composed ride. This is a dependable, honest vehicle that requires nothing but a new driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
